                <p class="feature-product">Replace ASP.NET Core's non-standard form validation with
                    standard HTML5 validation.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/Finbuckle/Finbuckle.Html5Validation"
                   class="btn btn-primary">Learn more</a>
